{"tid":1042574,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"韋史密夫辭演《自殺特攻2》","createTime":"2019-03-01T15:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T01:33:04.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"6cf9c5b5b6b3464ea013789deb7604989e0cca91","tid":1042574,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/ArticleBase/big/28419/116299.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2FArticleBase%2Fbig%2F28419%2F116299.jpg&h=fcfff6e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDeadshot係《自殺特攻》中數一數二成功嘅角色，不過最近有報導指，男星韋史密夫因為檔期問題辭演《自殺特攻2》Deadshot一角。<br />\n據Variety稱，韋史密夫同電影公司係「和平分手」，雙方仍保持良好關係。續集由《銀河守護隊》導演James Gunn接手拍攝，最初網上有傳聞指續集會起用全新班底，但後來消息更正指至少韋史密夫同瑪歌羅比將會回歸。然而，現在韋史密夫離隊，原班人馬幾乎全部換走，瑪歌羅比未必會演出續集。《自殺特攻2》定於2021年8月6日開放。"},{"pid":"da3808b5f172ac12704518dd4b3b651545bb6a68","tid":1042574,"uid":75050,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"套套拍一集就換人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96aec86967b263a18f4a28e1ad11357066182e4c","tid":1042574,"uid":141210,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T16:00:58.000Z","msg":"雖然will好正<br />\n但呢個角色，笠呢個頭邊個認到係咩人演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FC20xWb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFC20xWb.png&h=20045076&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3fe1d0fdb3c81c348ef8f75f68ebcb4288f9b39","tid":1042574,"uid":44674,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"夾硬改做黑人都已經搞笑"},{"pid":"9cbc6e93e1762c1f8d54cc1e4f5cad001431cfc0","tid":1042574,"uid":75050,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"da3808b5f172ac12704518dd4b3b651545bb6a68","tid":1042574,"uid":75050,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"套套拍一集就換人<img src=\"/assets/f